      "parameters": {
        "color": 7,
        "width": 1504,
        "height": 928,
        "content": "# üí¨ Chat with Your Trello Board (n8n + OpenAI)\n\nTurn your Trello board into a conversational assistant. This workflow pulls your board ‚Üí lists ‚Üí cards, aggregates the context, and lets you **ask natural-language questions** (‚Äúwhat‚Äôs overdue?‚Äù, ‚Äúsummarize In Progress‚Äù, ‚Äúwhat changed this week?‚Äù). OpenAI reasons over the live board data and replies with concise answers or summaries. Great for standups, planning, and quick status checks‚Äîwithout opening Trello.\n\n"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
